title: Gared O'Donnell from Hawks & Dove/Planes Mistaken For Stars
itunes:title: Gared O'Donnell from Hawks & Dove/Planes Mistaken For Stars
description:
I had the opportunity to have a very honest and open chat with Gared O'Donnell, the lead vocalist from Planes Mistaken For Stars/Hawks & Doves. We spoke about the need to create art, how life can mirror art and how he was raised in bars. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
